description: The list of the test sets.

parameters.name: sortBy
parameters.description: The sort order for the list of test sets. Specifies whether to sort the test sets by name or by the time they were last updated. Specifies whether to sort in ascending or descending order.

nested_params.name: attribute
nested_params.description: Specifies whether to sort the test sets by name or by the time they were last updated.

nested_params.name: order
nested_params.description: Specifies whether to sort in ascending or descending order.

nested_items.name: testSets
nested_items.description: The selected test sets in a list of test sets.

nested_items.name: testSetId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the test set.

nested_items.name: testSetName
nested_items.description: The name of the test set.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: The description of the test set.

nested_items.name: modality
nested_items.description: Specifies whether the test set contains written or spoken data.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the test set.

nested_items.name: roleArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of an IAM role that has permission to access the test set.

nested_items.name: numTurns
nested_items.description: The number of turns in the test set.

nested_items.name: storageLocation
nested_items.description: Contains information about the location at which the test set is stored.

nested_items.name: s3BucketName
nested_items.description: The name of the Amazon S3 bucket in which the test set is stored.

nested_items.name: s3Path
nested_items.description: The path inside the Amazon S3 bucket where the test set is stored.

nested_items.name: kmsKeyArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of an Amazon Web Services Key Management Service (KMS) key for encrypting the test set.

nested_items.name: creationDateTime
nested_items.description: The date and time at which the test set was created.

nested_items.name: lastUpdatedDateTime
nested_items.description: The date and time at which the test set was last updated.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: A token that indicates whether there are more results to return in a response to the ListTestSets operation. If the nextToken field is present, you send the contents as the nextToken parameter of a ListTestSets operation request to get the next page of results.
